data.description: Welcome to your new home in the Shadowlawn Community where tranquility and convenience converge. This residence boasts 2392 square feet of carefully designed living space, featuring 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, all nestled within a serene and quiet neighborhood. As you step through the inviting entryway, you enter into the generously proportioned living room that is perfect for intimate gatherings and entertaining. Off the back is an expansive bonus space that offers endless possibilities - whether you envision a cozy den, a versatile game room, a serene family retreat, or even your own personal gym, this space is ready to be tailored to your desires. There is also another extra space off the laundry room that could be used as an office. Indulge in the luxury of the extra-large primary bedroom, a true oasis of relaxation. The primary bathroom features a Roman tub that offers the option of a soothing stand-up shower or a sumptuously indulgent soak. Step outside into your private sanctuary - an oversized privacy-fenced backyard. Here, you'll find a convenient shed, placed to house all your lawn equipment and essentials. The heart of this home is the kitchen, from the extra-tall cabinets that offer abundant storage, to the sleek gas stove and convenient double oven, every detail has been carefully considered. The underlit cabinets create an ambiance of refined elegance, while the additional pantry space provides even more practicality to this space. Natural light pours in through large picture windows that adorn the front of the house. A true gem in a sought-after location, this home offers an exceptional blend of tranquility, and privacy, priced lower per square foot at $135.86 a square foot, than the comps, Priced to sell fast! Schedule your showing today! ***** Seller offering a $3500 flooring allowance!!!
